  "text": "Previous studies have investigated different methods to provide emotional intelligence to computers. Among those methods, facial image based emotion recognition is the most widely used method since this method can recognize a wide range of emotion types [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Another approach is the speech signal analysis that determines the human emotion by analysing the patterns in the speech signal [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . In addition, direct examination of the person is one of the most sophisticated ways for human emotion recognition [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . These methods use different types of bio-signals to continuously",
